{"tid":1076461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[貨車佬又on9贏]綠van撞貨車尾板　半邊車身劏開","createTime":"2019-03-25T00:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T07:47:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d631692c9f29b872d86ad1bf4c651afbbef4b3cf","tid":1076461,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190325/bkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190325%2Fbkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001.html&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6cIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=19bc9a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190325/bkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田大圍發生驚險車禍，貨車尾板劏開小巴車身。昨日（24日）晚上11時許，<strong>一輛貨車停泊在美田邨香粉寮街路旁，姓陸(35歲)司機開啟升降尾板整理車上貨物時，疑部分尾板過度伸出馬路，適時一輛已停止載客的專線小巴駛至，意外撞向尾板。</strong><br />\n<br />\n由於撞擊力極大，小巴由左車頭至車門的車身當場被劏開，嚴重毀爛，貨車更被推撞下，全車橫擺，車尾撞及停泊在其右側的一輛七人車，車頭則撞向其左旁的一輛貨車，俱受不同程度損毀。意外中，貨車司機猝不及防下，在車斗上失平衡跌倒，手部受傷，需送院治理，警方聯絡到被波及貨車姓李(38歲)司機及七人車姓黃(51歲)司機返現場了解，調查肇事原因。據現場消息指涉事姓吳(67歲)小巴司機稱，當時正準備到附近泊車收工，幸車上無乘客，否則後果不堪設想。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190325/photo/bkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190325085435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190325%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190325085435&h=60b44586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190325/photo/bkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190325085435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190325%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190325001606941-0325_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190325085435&h=38aaecae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73cddc8559013a3e71b5e17996868a1173b8e5bb","tid":1076461,"uid":53378,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201